{
  "text": "It is now clear that ischemic postconditioning reduces: infarct size, post-ischemic arrhythmias, apoptosis, endothelial-dysfunction and -activation. However, it is not clear if it can reduce myocardial stunning [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] (Fig. 1) .",
